rComments: She was really nice and friendly during lecture! She explained topic really well and was always making sure people understand before continue. Really a shame that not many taking this course.

Really great prof! Turned out to be a fun course and she explained concepts very clearly with lots of examples and useful slides. Posts everything but audio from lectures so it's easy to catch up if you've missed a lecture. Takes questions during and sometimes after class and has office hours 2x a week. Very caring, and overall nice prof!

I really liked her! Unfortunately I don't think she's teaching 258 again. Her slides were really clear and she always went over things often to make sure that everybody understood. She's really nice. Often people wouldn't speak up in class though, so if you can answer her questions you should, otherwise she assumes people are having trouble.
